Welcome to OrlampaAuto! 

Visiting Orlando, Tampa, or Clearwater? We are here to make sure your trip goes as seamless as possible! If you are looking for a reliable host, then look no further! We love the vehicles in our fleet and are extremely excited to offer them to you. 

Why should you book with us?

- We are available nearly 24/7 to help out with anything you might possibly need.

- Your safety is our priority! Every vehicle is properly maintained and thoroughly cleaned before/after every trip.

- All of our cars have instant booking turned on so you can be sure to guarantee a vehicle for your upcoming trip! 

- Whether it's 2pm or 2am you can book at any time that's most convenient for you! We offer 24/7 bookings! 

- We deliver all across Central Florida! 

If you're still on the fence, check out our reviews! We pride ourselves in ensuring you have an amazing, simple, and straightforward experience. We know the last thing you want to do on vacation is worry about your rental car! 

- Jake

My husband and I are FL-born and raised. Johans and I are from two of the most popular cities to visit in FL: Tampa and Orlando. We have a few cars that we truly love and decided to share them on the platform, which allows our clients to enjoy our favorite rides. Considering they are our favorites, we have plenty of recommendations of where and how they can be used. Johans and I are available via messaging throughout your trip. If you want to get more out of your trip and are looking for things to do, message us! As Florida locals, we love to recommend places to go.
